  "translations": {
    "en": "He said: \"O Mayassar! What do you say about a person who worships God with the same faith as yours, and has sins like other people, except that he avoids the major sins?\" I said: \"What can I say while I am in your presence?\" He said: \"Say! For I am the one who commands you to speak.\" I said: \"In Paradise.\" He said: \"Perhaps you hesitate to say he is in Paradise?\" I said: \"No.\" He said: \"Then do not hesitate, for he is in Paradise.\"",
    "ur": "\"اے میسر! اس شخص کے بارے میں تم کیا کہتے ہو... فرمایا: تو تامل نہ کرو، کیونکہ وہ جنت میں ہے۔\"",
    "tr": "\"Ey Meyser! ... Dedi: 'O halde çekinme, çünkü o cennettedir.'\"",
    "fa": "\"ای میسر! ... فرمود: پس شرم نکن، زیرا او در بهشت است.\"",
    "id": "\"Wahai Mayassar! ... Beliau berkata: 'Maka janganlah ragu, karena ia di surga.'\"",
    "bn": "\"হে মায়াসসার! ... তিনি বললেন: 'তাহলে সংকোচ করো না, কারণ সে জান্নাতে।'\"",
    "es": "\"¡Oh Mayassar! ... Dijo: 'Entonces no dudes, pues él está en el Paraíso.'\"",
    "fr": "\"Ô Mayassar ! ... Il dit : 'Alors n'hésite pas, car il est au Paradis.'\"",
    "de": "\"O Mayassar! ... Er sagte: 'Dann zögere nicht, denn er ist im Paradies.'\"",
    "ru": "\"О Майассар! ... Он сказал: 'Тогда не колеблись, ибо он в Раю.'\"",
    "zh": "\"哦，迈亚萨尔！...他说：'那就不要犹豫，因为他确实在天堂。'\""
  }
